<h1>Transliteration</h1>

<p>Greek is indicated by the language shift <code>%grc</code>.</p>

<p>Greek may be entered in Unicode without any special indication to
the ATF processor; we define an ASCII transliteration as well since it
may be easier for some users to employ.</p>

<table class="sixty">
<tr><td>alpha</td><td>α</td><td>a</td></tr>
<tr><td>beta</td><td>β</td><td>b</td></tr>
<tr><td>gamma</td><td>γ</td><td>g</td></tr>
